{
  "info": {
    "name": "SmartInventory Mobile API — Full",
    "description": "Complete .NET mobile API collection covering all 9 controllers.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import environment: `smartinventory-mobile.postman_environment.json`\n2. Select environment \"SmartInventory Mobile - Local\"\n3. Start with **Login** → runs all subsequent requests\n\n## Folders\n- **01-Auth** — register, login, verify, password reset, profile\n- **02-Supervisor** — admin user management (requires Supervisor role)\n- **03-Home** — dashboard aggregation\n- **04-Lookups** — categories, departments, rooms, stats, barcode\n- **05-Products** — CRUD, search, scan, status, location, history\n- **06-Assets** — batch operations\n- **07-Sync** — offline sync queue\n- **08-Reports** — PDF fiche/journal, QR code downloads\n- **09-Notifications** — list, read, delete\n\n## Variables (auto-populated)\n- `{{token}}` — set by Login\n- `{{productId}}` — set by GET /products",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      { "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 — Login (sets token)",
      "description": "Authenticates and stores the access token in `{{token}}`. All subsequent requests use collection-level Bearer auth.",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "exec": [
              "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test(\"Login succeeds\", () => {",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
              "    pm.expect(jsonData.data.accessToken).to.not.be.empty;",
              "});",
              "if (jsonData.success && jsonData.data.accessToken) {",
              "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"token\", jsonData.data.accessToken);",
              "}"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["auth", "login"]
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "name": "01 — Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "POST Register",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
